title: From iCub to humanoids: Generative Bionics raises $81M
description:
Generative Bionics plans to unveil its first humanoid robot, built for production environments, at CES in Las Vegas.

The post From iCub to humanoids: Generative Bionics raises $81M appeared first on The Robot Report.
